Dia.03 If White Plays
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If it is White's turn, he also plays the hane and connects which is sente.
\par
\par When it is sente for both players it is called \cf1\b double sente endgame\cf0\b0 .
\par In case it is gote for both players, it is called \cf1\b double gote endgame\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par
\par
